30. Write a function replace_vowels(s, ch) that replaces all vowels in s with character ch.

def replace_vowels(s, ch) #assuming s is a string
   str1 = ""
   for x in s:
      if(x == 'a' or x == 'i' or x == 'o' or x == 'u'):
         str1 += 'ch'
      else
         str1 += x 
